The paper deals with the problem of event recognition in aerial videos, which involves computer vision and machine learning techniques. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The use of unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs) also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning networks, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
